ed on PA application unit in different environments. The high-resolution remote sensing images provide basic data for the realization of this idea, and the conversion technology of multi-scale data provides better support for the spatial inference of fine soil attribute information. In the future, we will carry out experiments in larger areas to further improve the efficiency of application, and plan to expand this study to consider three-dimensional soil property prediction.},
